subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: TAMPA, Fla. (AP) — No. 16 Tennessee overcame injuries, academic suspensions and the impending departure of two key assistant coaches to beat No. 18 Wisconsin, 21-17, in the Outback Bowl on Tuesday. The victory gave the Volunteers their first 10-win season since 2004.
